text: Ðis is þara tyn hida boc æt macaniæ & æt Suttunæ Wylle þe eadred cing gebocode æþelwearde his þegnæ on ece yrfæ.
Ter duodenas segetes cum bis quinis prati jugeribus, quod anglice dicitur XXXVIæcera yrþ landes &Xæceras mæde.
Ðis synt þa fif hida æt Maccanige.
Ðonne ligþ bæ norþan þam porte XXXVI æcera yrþ landes.
And binnan þam porte fram geast geate on norþ healfe strete.
Þonne hebbe ic hit egþer ge binnan porte.
Eall swa æþelwold bisceop hit ær hæfde.
